🚀 Day 2 – Variables & Arithmetic Operator (+) in Java
🔹 Rule 1: String + String → String (Concatenation)

String s1 = "Hello"; 
String s2 = "World";
String result = s1 + s2;

System.out.println(result);

Output
HelloWorld


🔹 Rule 2: String + int → String

String text = "Age: ";
int age = 20;

System.out.println(text + age);

Output
Age: 20


🔹 Rule 3: int + int → Arithmetic Addition
int a = 10;
int b = 20;

int sum = a + b;

System.out.println(sum);
 Output
30





